Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆 我问你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会不会突然想开一个后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多此一问
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提起这个 我就想到希望受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要受欢迎的正是我 豆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里很凉爽舒适呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你沙耶师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.11,0:02:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱是什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想了解恋爱的滋味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小喵咪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想了解恋爱的滋味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么没关系 为什么要靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤你难道是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛 沙耶师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 不是草莓味的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苹果味吗 菠萝味?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:00.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是樱桃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从彩虹上而来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又小又圆的樱桃之诗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱的可爱的恋爱滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.35,0:04:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱桃之诗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是沙耶师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连「恋爱的滋味」这么难的脑筋急转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也能立刻答对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是脑筋急转弯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:31.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然想受欢迎的椰子 现在究竟应该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请回答 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前集提过 女孩子喜欢占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就掐准这点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Orion公司的相机盒子糖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不上不下的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 这摆在动物园小卖部卖的包裝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 它很有粗点心的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:04:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这个玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实可以用来占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.19,0:05:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 占卜明天的运势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目标是粉色「受异性欢迎」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要掉落粉色 我们明天就会大受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.00,0:05:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来定会一片粉红
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 豆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 鉴定血统的时刻到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK 豆来打先锋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用力太猛结果倒出来两个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 两个都是粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放回去一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不用两个吧 豆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居 居然都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你拿了唯二的粉色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 你好好想一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么先把我推出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.02,0:06:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你心里应该这么想过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能第一就掉落粉色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我抽掉一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抽出粉色的机率就会提高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也注意到这点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.87,0:06:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本想在我坠机后说一句「可惜」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你脆弱的内心导致的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.02,0:07:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想开个后宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是友军啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是粉色的糖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我装作吃掉 其实在手指里夹了一颗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.76,0:07:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样来我们明天就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大受欢迎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大受欢迎 大受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始 大受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.33,0:08:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}今天明天后天都能大受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩发什么病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受欢迎 受欢迎 开后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦哦 一起来开后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}男孩子凑一起就会瞎胡闹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,沙耶和萤？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果真的到了不得不进行抉择的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我听听你的答案吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等着你的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:09:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底闹什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那羞耻的诗意表现是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诗意？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想 从彩虹上而来什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是写在包装里的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也说不出那么羞耻的台词啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 也对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.79,0:09:33.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些诗句很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是樱桃之诗为什么要和恋爱挂钩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为「恋爱是酸酸甜甜的」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得太妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.06,0:09:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难 难道 萤也喜欢椰子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沙耶师有过酸酸甜甜的经验吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:26.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 我也说不准有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸薯片君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 你的脑洞又塌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:55.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想什么心事呢 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咖啡都要凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是把萤绑得太紧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑 绑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天吃粗点心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让叔叔伤脑筋的坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.35,0:11:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}那个 椰子 这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么突然提起这个 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实昨天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道因为你每天都来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没办法去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还说这都怪我没有下定决心继承
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs-1}这种糟糕的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.48,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说绑 我以为要触发18禁情节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:11:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我可没想歪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再装
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想歪 你有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.41,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果店没有人继承
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就认为自己阻碍了萤的自由是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.05,0:12:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想啊 爸爸总是强迫我看店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我也有许多想做却做不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是能理解她的心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤她不像是会被束缚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本无法想象她被剥夺自由的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我重新泡咖啡 沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.46,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等着你的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那么纠结 就去和萤谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想知道她的想法 直接问不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中场暂停 时机好巧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有吸烟区吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤她抽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可还有其他坐吸烟区的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是森永牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:57.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为什么要特意在吸烟区吃牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前曾将牛奶糖当烟草的替代品来宣传
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:13.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本牛奶糖是成人商品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 以前卖得很贵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:23.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从明治时代到大正时代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个大福和一颗牛奶糖似乎是等价的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:32.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还有其他特别的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年日本人还没习惯乳制品的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶糖曾经被嫌弃说「一股奶臭味」卖得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会提出烟草替代品这种战略形象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.57,0:14:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 不过喜欢牛奶糖的人其实不少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中还有福泽谕吉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶糖太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 糖吃完了 我还要买
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了一万円
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.39,0:15:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解说得很详细嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是不深入 接着说给我听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的挑衅都写脸上了 椰子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.03,0:15:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的知识储备已经掏空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么 还能说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九的段数还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定是要说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开大招啊 椰子小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森永牛奶糖至今推出多种囗味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南高梅 红豆味 抹茶味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这其中还有与我的绰号同名的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椰子味牛奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得不错 我给好评
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不去追吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有话要和萤谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好险 突然下那么大的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过萤她去哪儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在雨中湿身的感觉的确很棒 但我很想吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佐久间罐装水果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般的包装打开一次就不能复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这牢固的盖子可以抵抗任何人的入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐久间罐装水果糖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样来就不用担心被淋湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤的入侵被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西应该
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用硬币 这样撬开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到使用大家随身携带的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能如此轻易打开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是想问你以前怎么打开的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠气势
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气势…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功率还是挺高的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也有不能如意的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:55.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想做什么 九君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:19:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想把薄荷糖放回里面去 拿出其他糖来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到了不喜欢的也不许放回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:23.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,薄荷糖也挺好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.27,0:19:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么大家尝都不尝就嫌弃薄荷糖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明薄荷糖好吃到出单品了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动是一切之本 必须得先尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 萤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话要对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天萤在车站说会等着我的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我认为还是尽快给出答复比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为只要我尽早决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤就不用每天来我家 被束缚在小镇上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤想创建世界第一的点心制造商
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这么拖着 岂不是妨碍你的梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还害你不能巡游粗点心店
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行想去就能去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然我们说走就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 突然邀请我去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 创建世界第一点心制造商不是梦想而是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天前往鹿田粗点心的确是为了说服你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对热爱粗点心的人来说 这是最快乐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.74,0:21:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你认真为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:07.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水果糖的盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.21,0:21:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候用气势也无法打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 然后我就用硬币打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 我不懂你想表达的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天晴了 九君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.49,0:21:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 那个车站没车来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.76,0:22:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 到时候车就会来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.18,0:22:07.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的啊
